examples.en: At the hospital, the endocrinologist was brisk, but kind.

examples.en: She now is being treated by an endocrinologist and a gastroenterologist.

examples.en: The only local endocrinologist is not able to absorb so many new patients.

examples.en: Nobody follows the Mediterranean diet in the Mediterranean unless told to do so by an endocrinologist.
